I am almost done with my obsession over Jianghua, and ready for the BL market again.  Then find it extremely difficult to have anything to read.
When I say "almost done", it means that he no longer drives me nuts and keeps me waking up to 2am something in the morning watching his series and thinking about him.

It was so much fun when re-reading the old records of Chinese BL stories.  I keep forgetting what was read before, and some of the stories which I didn't like before but want to re-read it again, such as Zhuquehen's Broken Flute.
